    "description": "We at Swiggy Digital Technologies are looking for an experienced Backend Developer based out of Ranchi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Swiggy Digital Technologies:\nSwiggy Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Optimize application performance and ensure high availability\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in CI/CD\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in TypeScript\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Ranchi, Jharkhand, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Swiggy Digital Technologies!",
